  "title": "purchasing manager assistant",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li>Responsible for purchasing raw materials from overseas.</li><li>quality control and checking of incoming material.</li><li>be responsible to get lowest price of all materials.</li><li>frequent travel to Asia contries is a must</li><li>Manage contractors/suppliers on quality, compliance with engineering drawings; applicable code and standards, and construction schedule and cost.</li><li>Point of contact for government/statutory authorities, consultants, clients, suppliers etc.</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li>At least 5 years of relevant experince in construction.</li><li>A diploma/degree in Construction Engineering or relevant certifications.</li><li>Good interpersonal skills and communication skills.</li><li></li></ul><p>To apply, please include the following details inside your CV for faster processing:</p><ul><li>Reasons for leaving each past & current employment</li><li>Salary drawn for each past & current employment</li><li>Expected Salary</li><li>Earliest availability date</li></ul>",
